      "content": "1-2 units feels a bit vague though. if my sensitivity factor is 1:50, then mathematically to drop 85 points (from 185 to 100) that would be 1.7 units. but since i'm working and don't want to risk a crash later, should i just round up to 2 units to be safe and get it down faster? i feel like if i dont hit it now it'll just keep rising.",
